==English==
===Pronunciation===
dish·wash·er·a·ble /dish-"wo-sh&r-&-b&l/ 

===Etymology===
[[dishwasher]] + [[-able]]

===Adjective===
'''dishwasherable'''
# [[dishwasher-safe]]; able to be placed safely in a dishwasher for cleaning
#:''All the parts of the deep fryer are '''dishwasherable'''.''

